examples: The call to jury duty was sent to my legal domicile ; too bad I was on vacation at the time.

definitions.definition: A residence at a particular place accompanied with an intention to remain there for an unlimited time; a residence accepted as a final abode.

The zodiac sign over which a planet (a term which in astrology includes the Sun and Moon) is considered to have especially strong influence; the planet is called the sign's ruling planet or sign ruler .
